00:24:29,238 --> 00:24:30,738
-Anything today? -The characters for love and song

380
00:24:30,738 --> 00:24:32,738
make "Love Letter". Oh, my beloved Ms. Sato.

381
00:24:32,738 --> 00:24:34,238
That's actually pretty decent.

